Source: vigilo-collector
Section: vigilo
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Vigilo Team <contact@projet-vigilo.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 5), perl-doc
Standards-Version: 3.7.2

Package: vigilo-collector
Architecture: all
Suggests: vigilo-collector-doc
Depends:
 nagios2 | nagios3,
 ${perl:Depends},
 libnet-snmp-perl,
 libcrypt-des-perl,
 libdigest-hmac-perl,
 libdigest-sha1-perl
Recommends: nsca
Description: Centralized collector plugin for Nagios
 This plugin collects SNMP data for an equipment
 using as few requests as possible. It then computes
 states from that data and forwards both states and
 other (performance) data to other Vigilo components.

