Architecture: all
Section: doc
Depends: ${sphinxdoc:Depends} ${misc:Depends}
Description: Centralized collector plugin for Nagios (documentation)
 This plugin collects SNMP data for an equipment
 using as few requests as possible. It then computes
 states from that data and forwards both states and
 other (performance) data to other Vigilo components.
 .
 This package contains documentation about vigilo-collector.

